<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥٥٦)</span> -<span class="c5"> (حديث:</span> " إذا أمرتكم بأمر فأتوا منه ما استطعتم <span class="c1">" <span class="c2">(ص ١٣٢)</span> .<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
